As the shuttle came around to look for a landing pad, the two scouts split
off and began scanning for signatures.  Depthcharge landed at the site of
the fighting and looked down at the incapactitated jet.

&quot;We have one pred, either in stasis lock or dead.  Requesting an
extraction... wait a minute...&quot;

He had dropped his guard for a minute and that was all the time needed for
the giant dog to attack.  His jaws grabbing onto a piece of his shoulder,
Depthcharge fell backward onto the ground.

&quot;Report....  report.....&quot; said Guardia into the radio, then turning to the
pilot.  &quot;Drop us at his location then land somewhere safe.&quot;

Meanwhile....

Ravenchief flew over the back alleys around the government buidling,
scanning for signatures.
